title: Call of Duty 1.5 Wallhack
description:
Punkbuster Proof call of duty wallhack tested on version 1.5 and virus free.

|---------------------------------------|
|            FuRy 1.1			|
|---------------------------------------|


This hack was based off of N7&#039;s oglcod hack, wich had NoFog, Wallhack, and a Crosshair.
I modified it to have 3 types of Crosshairs, and colored sky (next version), and also
to be PB Proof. This hack is designed to be PB Proof, and whenever the previous version
gets detected, I will release another version of this hack. This hack is NOT a part of my
xBot series, as I have stopped making xBot for the public.

Hacks Included In This Version
================================|
				|
Wallhack   ----- On by Default	|
NoFog      ----- ALT+F1		|
Crosshair  ----- ALT+F2		|
Crosshair2 ----- ALT+F3		|
Crosshair3 ----- ALT+F4		|
				|
================================|

Directions:

Extract The Loader, oglcod.dll, and oglcod.ini to anywhere you want. Doubleclick on the
loader, and enjoy.
